Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=God the Only Doer
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
It is, in fact, the indefinable power of the Lord that ordains,
sustains and controls everything that happens. Why then, should we
languish tormented by vexatious thought, saying ‘This wise to act; but
no, that way ...’, instead of meekly but happily submitting ourselves
to that Power?
